---
title: Seared Tuna with Thyme-Roasted Summer Veggies and Lemon Aioli
description: If you have a grill, tuna steaks are great for it! Searing for just a couple minutes per side ensures that the centers remain bright red and delicious. A medley of roasted summer veggies completes this light and seasonal summer meal.
